{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/at-rule-blacklist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/media-feature-name-whitelist/","description":"custom-media-pattern 指定自定义媒体查询名的模式。 选项 regex|string 字符串将被翻译成一个正则表达式，就像 new RegExp(yourString) ———— 所以一定要正确转义。 给定字符串： 以下模式被视为违规： 以下模式不被视为违规：","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"custom-media-pattern\"><a href=\"#custom-media-pattern\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>custom-media-pattern</h1>\n<p>指定自定义媒体查询名的模式。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">custom</span>-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> --foo (max-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">30em</span>);\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**             ↑\n * 这种模式 */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"选项\"><a href=\"#%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>选项</h2>\n<p><code>regex|string</code></p>\n<p>字符串将被翻译成一个正则表达式，就像 <code>new RegExp(yourString)</code> ———— 所以一定要正确转义。</p>\n<p>给定字符串：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\"><span class=\"hljs-string\">\"foo-.+\"</span></code></pre>\n<p>以下模式被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">custom</span>-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> --bar (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">30em</span>);</code></pre>\n<p>以下模式<em>不</em>被视为违规：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">custom</span>-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> --foo-bar (min-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">30em</span>);</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/custom-media-pattern.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/custom-media-pattern/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/custom-media-pattern/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/custom-media-pattern/index.html.f9ead325b36056f19a2857af7eafbfbd.json"}